<h2>What's new in 0.1.6</h2><ul>
<li>Publish to an existing Vercel project by picking it from a list, not just creating a new one.</li>
<li>If a new project name is already taken on Vercel, you now see it right away, with a one-tap way to publish into that project instead.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
